videos.description: Army quarterback Kelvin Hopkins Jr. sells a play-action fake and zips it to a lone Jordan Asberry, who chugs into the end zone for a 41-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Army QB finds wide-open target for 41-yard TD

videos.description: San Jose State quarterback Montel Aaron fumbles as he is spun down by Max Regan, as James Nachitgal scoops the loose ball and brings it 52 yards to the end zone for an Army touchdown.
videos.headline: Army takes fumble back 52 yards for TD
